          <div class="about-badge" aria-hidden="true"><span>About Me</span></div>
          <div class="about-content">
            <p itemprop="description">My name is Doha Jaafari, and I'm passionate about User Experience Design and creating digital solutions that are simple, useful, and human-centered.</p>
            <p>Curious, creative, and organized, I love understanding real user needs and turning their problems into smooth and intuitive experiences.</p>
            <p>I value user research, clarity, and visual consistency in every project I work on.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
