        <div class="experience-item" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WorkExperience">
          <div class="experience-left">
            <h3 itemprop="roleName">UX/UI Designer Intern — IT Company</h3>
            <p class="date"><time itemprop="startDate">August 2023</time> — 1 month</p>
          </div>
          <div class="experience-right">
            <p itemprop="description">During this internship, I worked on redesigning the company's website by identifying usability issues and proposing solutions to improve the user experience. I created wireframes and interactive prototypes to visualize the new design and collaborated with the team to ensure a clear and intuitive interface.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="experience-item" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WorkExperience">
          <div class="experience-left">
            <h3 itemprop="roleName">UX Designer — Moroccan Customs Administration, Rabat</h3>
            <p class="date"><time itemprop="startDate">March 2025</time> – <time itemprop="endDate">May 2025</time> — 2 months</p>
          </div>
          <div class="experience-right">
            <p itemprop="description">I contributed to several UX projects, including the redesign of the intranet and key pages of the official website. I also created an educational interactive game for the Customs Museum. My work involved user research (personas, empathy maps, journey maps), wireframing, and prototyping to improve usability and overall clarity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
